        <h1 class="gridMiniHeadline alignCenter colorPrimary">Volunteer & Intern</h1>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- The Hub -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/the-hub-01.png" alt="Woman with a Camera" />
            <a href="https://thehub.io" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                The Hub
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                The Hub is a platform for all Creative Individuals who live up in the North and constantly look for opportunities. It is a place that helps you
