                all those who are willing to study a foreign language abroad and have an educational journey in their life.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- ESL Languages  -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/esl-languages-01.png" alt="Woman Reading in a Coffee Shop" />
